reviewText: Ok, so I bought them because I had those infernal Disney songs in my head. But, these films were good and for the price you can't beat packaging disk like this. Too bad it didn't have Beauty and the Beast in it though.

It was quick and easy. Rather than wait for days and hope your the highest bidder on ebay I chose the easier route. After I purchased the dvd's go to my home 2 days later. No hassle nor dealing with a seller that takes there sweet time. Movies were bnib, emamaculate! Would recommend over ebay
